<HEADLINE> Asian Business Information Website Propels Phenomenal Growth </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, May 13 (Xinhua) -- A leading on-line provider of
free financial information on Asia's listed companies reported on
Wednesday a hefty 1,200 percent increase of usage of its Internet
service in 15 months.
</P>
<P>
Provided by Investor Relations Asia, a Hong Kong-based on-line
financial service company, the website was accessed roughly 77,500
times in January 1997 and by March 1998 the figure jumped to over
930,000. Daily hits now average well above 30,000, the company
announced Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The website, irasia.com, was launched in late 1996. It posts
company profiles, annual reports, interim reports, press releases
on close to 400 Hong Kong listed companies. It also provides data
of almost 2,000 companies listed in the Asia Pacific region.
</P>
</TEXT>
