<HEADLINE> WHO Elects New Director-General </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GENEVA, May 13 (Xinhua) -- Gro Harlem Brundtland, of Norway,
was elected the new director-general of the World Health
Organization (WHO) here on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
