annual session of the World Health Assembly, the highest governing
body of the United Nations specialized agency.
</P>
<P>
The annual meeting, the 51st of the kind, began Monday.
</P>
<P>
Brundtland was nominated to the post during the 101st session
of the WHO Executive Board in January. 
