10, according to a report Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The party's leader Chalerm Yubamrung and the other party MP,
Araya Chumduang, went to NAP office Tuesday to apply for
membership. The party has only two MPs in the House of
Representatives, the report said.
</P>
