Sierra Leonean President Ahmed Tejan Kabbah and ECOMOG Commander,
Major-General Timothy Shelpidi, NAN said.
</P>
<P>
Khobe has been named commander of the Sierra Leonean army by
President Kabbah and is now in charge of national security.
