technology bellwethers Dell Computer, Intel and Microsoft.
</P>
<P>
But the Russell 2000 index of smaller companies fell 0.77 to
476.13, and the small-company dominated American Stock Exchange
composite index fell 0.45 to 743.58.
</P>
<P>
The late advance came as the yield on the 30-year Treasury bond
fell back below 6 percent just one day after bobbing above that
psychologically important level. 
</P>
